Titolo: Magna Carta: The Phantom of Avalanche

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Magna Carta: The Phantom of Avalanche (마그나카르타 ~눈사태의 망령~), also known as just Magna Carta (마그나카르타), is a Korean role-playing video game developed and published by Softmax for Windows in 2001. It is the predecessor to the PlayStation 2 title, Magna Carta: Tears of Blood, and was the first installment in the Magna Carta series. It was never released outside of Korea.